      "content": "yeah, i checked the sync logic and it looks solid. it's just so frustrating because it feels so random. one minute everything is perfect, and the next it's just... broken, for no real reason. i've been staring at this for hours and it's starting to feel like the code is just playing tricks on me. is there anything else that could cause that kind of \"phantom\" behavior? something that just randomly messes up a clean process?",
